data.description: Making a move on this property, today!   Spend your days in this new build, the beautiful Grayhawk Wellington floor plan with 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, eat in kitchen, formal dining, an office with French doors, 2 story home situated in the middle of its 9.4 acres.  More than enough room in the gourmet kitchen to cook your favorite meals or head out to the extended covered game day porch with a wood burning fireplace to grill out on those cool evenings while enjoying family and friends. Additional bonus room upstairs to become your library, playroom, or extra family room.  Master is on the second floor with an electric fireplace and luxury en-suite! Mother in law suite downstairs with all additional bedrooms upstairs. This home is absolutely stunning and ready for move in! Will work with pre-approved buyers with and without realtors.
data.whatILove:
There are so many wonderful features to our home.  So much space to roam both in and out of the house.  Lots of storage throughout the house and garage. Brand new architectural shingled roofs on the house and garage as well as a face-lift to the exterior.  4 large bedrooms and a bonus room - with master on the main level. Bring your wood burning stove to save on energy bills in the winter and share a cozy evening in front of a roaring fire.  Custom kitchen cabinets provide much needed storage in any kitchen.  Just installed new 92% efficiency furnace and new well, bladder and switch, as well as cleaned the septic tank out.
Every mechanic will love the air compressor line within the 1000+ sf garage and the abundant space to work on all of their hobbies.  You can keep your "toys" covered under either of the two carports.  Kids will enjoy themselves for hours on end while playing on their wooden play set.  Room to roam around the property with your 4-wheelers or just sit back and enjoy the quiet and nighttime star-filled sky.
